WorkItem.Description:
HtmlAgilityPack.1.4.9 NuGet package has a bad file inside it: lib\sl3-wp\_._
The file has 0 size and a suspicious name _._
Opening HtmlAgilityPack.1.4.9 package with NuGet Package Explorer produces an error "File contains corrupted data". It also causes issues with Visual Studio if the solution is setup to resolve and download NuGet packages automatically.
